headline: NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield ADR SMA Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: For the quarter, NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield ADR SMA posted a return of 5.1% (Gross) and 4.3% (Net) while the broad market returned negative 1.8% as measured by the MSCI World Index.
